{"tid":2108375,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人睇過上流寄生族？古早味蛋糕嘅歷史會唔會重演","createTime":"2020-07-14T13:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T23:57:43.000Z","uid":237538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a77511b37d388fd282d6cbb1055e776ad00cdb8","tid":2108375,"uid":237538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:19:48.000Z","msg":"電影中金家父親金基澤(宋康昊飾)及前管家的丈夫都曾投資過台灣古早味蛋糕店，雖然只是一兩句台詞輕輕帶過，但這個設計卻不是巧合。<br />\n<br />\n2016年韓國開始流行古早味蛋糕，一年內就已有過百間店。不過其後韓國節目《小吃X檔案》爆料，這些古早味蛋糕沒有用新鮮雞蛋，更添加大量食用油，更傳出這些食店的經營者全是韓國人，令各店家業績大跌，最後倒閉收場。<br />\n<br />\n導演奉俊昊曾指特意加入金基澤賣古早味蛋糕失敗的設定，是為了呼應時事並呈現金家一家都是冒充者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://food.ulifestyle.com.hk/restaurant/news/detail/2561872/寄生上流炸醬麵-奧斯卡最佳電影-上流寄生族-暗藏彩蛋-一句提及古早味蛋糕的台詞都有隱喻\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Frestaurant%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2561872%2F%E5%AF%84%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%81%E7%82%B8%E9%86%AC%E9%BA%B5-%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%81%E5%AF%84%E7%94%9F%E6%97%8F-%E6%9A%97%E8%97%8F%E5%BD%A9%E8%9B%8B-%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%8A%E5%8F%A4%E6%97%A9%E5%91%B3%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%B0%E8%A9%9E%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E9%9A%B1%E5%96%BB&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuBFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=05f47f9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://food.ulifestyle.com.hk/restaurant/news/detail/2561872/寄生上流炸醬麵-奧斯卡最佳電影-上流寄生族-暗藏彩蛋-一句提及古早味蛋糕的台詞都有隱喻</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022ac13c903fe8a454834311f09fc0e91e69fc4b","tid":2108375,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a77511b37d388fd282d6cbb1055e776ad00cdb8","tid":2108375,"uid":237538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:19:48.000Z","msg":"電影中金家父親金基澤(宋康昊飾)及前